manifest.name: Previous Daily Note
manifest.description: Open the previous daily note. Unlike the "Daily notes" command "Open previous daily note", it opens the previous daily note starting from today, rather than the daily note currently open.
manifest.author: Marcos Talau

data.manifestValue: Open the previous daily note. Unlike the "Daily notes" command "Open previous daily note", it opens the previous daily note starting from today, rather than the daily note currently open.
data.communityListValue: Unlike the "Daily notes" command "Open previous daily note", it opens the previous daily note starting from today, rather than the daily note currently open. It also provides a ribbon icon and a command to perform this action.
